# Insulin Pegylated

## Overview

Polyethylene glycol-conjugated insulin with reduced immunogenicity and extended circulation time.

## Structure

| Property | Value |
| -------- | ----- |
| Name     | Insulin Pegylated |

## Mechanism of Action

PEG conjugation shields insulin from proteolytic degradation and immune recognition while reducing renal filtration rate.

